<div style="background-color: #007786; border-radius: 20px 20px 20px 20px; color: #000000; width: 80%; margin-left: 5%; margin-right: 5%; padding: 10px 10px 5px 10px;">

<p style="color: white; line-height: 1.5; margin-left: 10px; margin-right: 10px; font-size: 18px"><b>How Do Teachers Assess in Their Classrooms?</b></p>

<p style="color: white; line-height: 1.2; margin-left: 10px; margin-right: 10px; font-size: 18px">Post your ideas and read other educators' ideas on the forum! Click on the icon to the left to direct to our forum post.
</p>


